The modelling table is now ready. It contains the same core variables as Chapter 05, plus a practical regional grouping for the regimes exercise. That allows us to compare three increasingly flexible stories: one national relationship, one national relationship with department intercept shifts, and one set of relationships that can vary across broader regional contexts.
